
"J.A.R.V.I.S?" I mumbled.
"Yes miss?"
"Thank you. For being my friend. You're the only one I have."
"Well that's harsh." A voice came from the doorway. I became still and slowly looked up.
"Phil?"
Well how about that ending. This chapter has been by far my favourite one to write. I just love the scene involved and have actually been planning it for awhile now. I'm really happy with how it turned out.
